' UML图标题
title Cglib代理

class TeacherDao{
	+ {method} teach(): void
}

interface MethodInterceptor

class ProxyFactory implements MethodInterceptor{
	..Field..
	- {field} target: Object
	--Method--
	+ {method} proxyFactory(): void
	+ {method} getProxyInstance(): Object
	+ {method} intercept(): void
}
note right of ProxyFactory
1. getProxyInstance()给目标对象
   target创建一个代理对象。
2.重写intercept()方法，实现对被
   代理对象(目标对象)方法的调用。
end note

class Client

Client .up.> ProxyFactory
Client .left.> TeacherDao



